quests.desc: Welcome to another exciting session of TextWorld! Here is your task for today. Your first objective is to make an effort to move south. With that over with, retrieve the keycard from the table. After that, move east. Following that, make it so that the chest is unlocked with the keycard. After that, open the chest. Then, take the type 0 key from the chest. And then, check that the type 0 door is unlocked with the type 0 key. Then, open the type 0 door inside the cookery. Then, make an attempt to move south. And then, look and see that the type 0 door is closed. And if you do that, you're the winner!
